title: All you guys complaining about how much it takes to win games. This is how you do it.

embed.description: Every game is a story; visit the new League of Legends match history to check out how this one ends and share your own!

body:
if you were as good as me, anything is possible. 
{{sticker:slayer-jinx-wink}}

replies.body:
Try doing it in ranked in the solo queue, go on, I dare you.

THIS http://matchhistory.oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/#match-details/OC1/137107991/41839391?tab=overview is how you carry a ranked game at low ELO.

All I see is you getting carried by a Lucian and Veigar whilst attempting to troll, and if you were premade and doing this as a joke I can undestand that, but you kept your troll items for a solid 4 minutes before switching to a different set of troll items, then a different set again.
